Class MergeSpatialClusters

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParamsInitializer<ImageInitParams>, Provider<ObjectCollection>

    public class MergeSpatialClusters
extends MergeBase
    Merges spatially-adjacent objects using the DBScan clustering algorithm.

    The features passed to DBSCAN are based on:

    • Euclidian distance
    • an @{code eps} (max distance for neighborhood connection) where distance is less than maxDistanceCOG (calculated on XY resolution)
    Author:
    Owen Feehan
